$var reg 1 \ next_dp_orig $end

$scope module clk_div $end
$var parameter 32 ] SIZE $end
$var wire 1 - clk $end
$var wire 1 . n_rst $end
$var wire 1 ^ clear $end
$var wire 1 _ count_enable $end
$var wire 1 ` rollover_val [3] $end
$var wire 1 a rollover_val [2] $end
